main event: Two white objects were observed moving at high altitudes near Rodeo, New Mexico on September 5, 1965.
interesting points: The objects appeared to be about 25 feet in diameter and round in shape., The objects were observed for approximately 1 minute while they glided in a straight line., A local villager reported the sighting to the Air Force, indicating the objects were of an unidentified nature., Witnesses described seeing the objects change colors from white to light blue., The sighting occurred under clear sky conditions with no noise observed from the objects.
